      "description": "China's permanent residence permit (green card / Five-Star Card) in 2026 \u2014 full requirements across all four pathways: professional, spouse, investor, and long-stay. Documents, timeline, who qualifies.",
      "datePublished": "2026-05-27",
      "dateModified": "2026-05-27",
      "author": {
        "@id": "https://seresimmigration.com/#organization"
      },
      "publisher": {
        "@id": "https://seresimmigration.com/#organization"
      },
      "mainEntityOfPage": {
        "@type": "WebPage",
        "@id": "https://movetochinanow.com/china-permanent-residency-requirements-for-foreigners-2026"
      },
      "inLanguage": "en"
    },
    {
      "@type": "FAQPage",
      "mainEntity": [
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "Is 'China green card' the same as 'permanent residence permit'?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "Yes \u2014 'China green card', 'Chinese permanent residence permit', and 'Five-Star Card' all refer to the same document, officially called the Foreign Permanent Resident ID Card. The card is valid for 10 years and renewable. The Chinese government uses 'permanent residence permit' in formal documents; 'green card' is the popular Western shorthand."
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "Does permanent residency in China lead to Chinese citizenship?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "No \u2014 permanent residence and citizenship are entirely separate statuses. PR lets you live and work in China indefinitely without renewing your visa. Citizenship requires giving up your original passport (China does not allow dual citizenship) and is approved at the discretion of the Ministry of Public Security. Most foreign PR holders stay on PR indefinitely rather than naturalize."
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "Which PR route is easiest to qualify for in 2026?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "It depends entirely on your situation. The professional/employment route is the most common for working foreigners but has high salary and tax thresholds. The spouse route requires 5 consecutive years of marriage and residence. The investor route requires substantial capital tied up for 3+ years. There is no universally 'easiest' route \u2014 the right route is the one your circumstances actually fit. Book a free consultation to find out which applies to you."
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
};

const body = `<style data-draft-styles="true">
/* ============================================================
       DESIGN TOKENS & RESET
    ============================================================ */
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :host {
      --color-navy:       #0d1f3c;
      --color-navy-mid:   #1a3358;
      --color-navy-light: #2a4a70;
      --color-gold:       #c8922a;
      --color-gold-light: #e8ab3f;
      --color-cream:      #f5f1eb;
      --color-cream-dark: #ede7dc;
      --color-white:      #ffffff;
      --color-text:       #1c2a3a;
      --color-text-muted: #5a6a7a;
      --color-border:     #d5cfc6;
      --color-success:    #1e7d54;

      --font-heading: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;
      --font-body:    'Segoe UI', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;

      --radius-sm:  4px;
      --radius-md:  8px;
      --radius-lg:  16px;

      --shadow-card: 0 2px 12px rgba(13,31,60,0.09);
      --shadow-lift: 0 6px 28px rgba(13,31,60,0.14);

      --max-w: 1140px;
      --section-py: 80px;
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    :host > .editorContent {
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      color: var(--color-text);
      background: var(--color-cream);
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    img { max-width: 100%; display: block; }
    a { color: var(--color-gold); text-decoration: none; }
    a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

    .container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: var(--max-w);
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 24px;
    }

    /* ============================================================
       TYPOGRAPHY
    ============================================================ */
    h1, h2, h3, h4 {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      color: var(--color-navy);
      line-height: 1.25;
    }
    h1 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); }
    h2 { font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.25rem); }
    h3 { font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2vw, 1.4rem); }
    h4 { font-size: 1.05rem; }

    .section-label {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--color-gold);
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    p { margin-bottom: 1em; }
    p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

    /* ============================================================
       UTILITY
    ============================================================ */
    .text-balance { text-wrap: balance; }
    .text-muted { color: var(--color-text-muted); }

    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 13px 28px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
      border: 2px solid transparent;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s, transform 0.15s;
    }
    .btn:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); text-decoration: none; }
    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--color-gold);
      color: var(--color-white);
      border-color: var(--color-gold);
    }
    .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--color-gold-light); border-color: var(--color-gold-light); }
    .btn-outline {
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--color-white);
      border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
    }
    .btn-outline:hover { border-color: var(--color-white); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); }
    .btn-navy {
      background: var(--color-navy);
      color: var(--color-white);
      border-color: var(--color-navy);
    }
    .btn-navy:hover { background: var(--color-navy-mid); border-color: var(--color-navy-mid); }

    .badge {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 3px 10px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .badge-gold { background: var(--color-gold); color: var(--color-white); }
    .badge-navy { background: var(--color-navy); color: var(--color-white); }
    .badge-green { background: var(--color-success); color: var(--color-white); }
    .badge-outline { border: 1px solid var(--color-border); color: var(--color-text-muted); background: transparent; }

    .divider {
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--color-border);
      border: none;
      margin: 0;
    }

    /* ============================================================
       NAV
    ============================================================ */
    .nav {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 100;
      background: var(--color-navy);
      border-bottom: 3px solid var(--color-gold);
    }
    .nav-inner {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 0 24px;
      max-width: var(--max-w);
      margin: 0 auto;
      height: 62px;
    }
    .nav-logo {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .nav-logo-icon {
      width: 34px;
      height: 34px;
      background: var(--color-gold);
      border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .nav-logo-text {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      color: var(--color-white);
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .nav-logo-text span { color: var(--color-gold-light); }
    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 2px;
      list-style: none;
    }
    .nav-links a {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.78);
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      padding: 6px 12px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
      transition: color 0.15s, background 0.15s;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--color-white); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); }
    .nav-cta { margin-left: 16px; }
    .nav-hamburger {
      display: none;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 5px;
      background: none;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      padding: 6px;
    }
    .nav-hamburger span {
      display: block;
      width: 22px;
      height: 2px;
      background: var(--color-white);
      border-radius: 2px;
    }
    .mobile-menu {
      display: none;
      background: var(--color-navy-mid);
      padding: 16px 24px 20px;
    }
    .mobile-menu.open { display: block; }
    .mobile-menu a {
      display: block;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
      padding: 10px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .mobile-menu a:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .mobile-menu a:hover { color: var(--color-gold-light); }

    /* ============================================================
       HERO
    ============================================================ */
    .hero {
      background: var(--color-navy);
      background-image:
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 40%, rgba(200,146,42,0.08) 0%, transparent 60%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 10% 80%, rgba(42,74,112,0.4) 0%, transparent 50%);
      padding: 72px 0 80px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .hero::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      height: 3px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--color-gold), var(--color-gold-light), var(--color-gold));
    }
    .hero-inner {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 60px;
    }
    .hero-content { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }
    .hero-media { flex: 0 0 420px; }
    .hero-eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      background: rgba(200,146,42,0.15);
      border: 1px solid rgba(200,146,42,0.3);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 5px 14px;
      margin-bottom: 22px;
    }
    .hero-eyebrow-dot {
      width: 7px; height: 7px;
      background: var(--color-gold-light);
      border-radius: 50%;
    }
    .hero-eyebrow-text {
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--color-gold-light);
    }
    .hero h1 {
      color: var(--color-white);
      margin-bottom: 22px;
    }
    .hero h1 em {
      color: var(--color-gold-light);
      font-style: normal;
    }
    .hero-lead {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }
    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 42px;
    }
    .hero-stats {
      display: flex;
      gap: 32px;
      padding-top: 32px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
    }
    .hero-stat-value {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-size: 1.85rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--color-gold-light);
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .hero-stat-label {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
      margin-top: 4px;
    }

    /* Hero media: info card placeholder */
    .hero-card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .hero-card-header {
      background: var(--color-gold);
      padding: 16px 22px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }
    .hero-card-header-icon {
      width: 32px; height: 32px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    }
    .hero-card-header-title {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      color: var(--color-white);
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .hero-card-body { padding: 22px; }
    .route-pill {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 11px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    }
    .route-pill:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .route-pill-name {
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .route-pill-tag {
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      padding: 3px 9px;
      border-radius: 12px;
    }
    .tag-easy { background: rgba(30,125,84,0.25); color: #5ce0a0; }
    .tag-med  { background: rgba(200,146,42,0.25); color: var(--color-gold-light); }
    .tag-hard { background: rgba(180,50,50,0.2); color: #f08080; }

    /* ============================================================
       TRUST BAR
    ============================================================ */
    .trust-bar {
      background: var(--color-cream-dark);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      padding: 18px 0;
    }
    .trust-bar-inner {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 32px;
    }
    .trust-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 9px;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--color-navy);
    }
    .trust-item-icon {
      width: 28px; height: 28px;
      background: var(--color-navy);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    /* ============================================================
       SECTION SHARED
    ============================================================ */
    .section { padding: var(--section-py) 0; }
    .section-alt { background: var(--color-white); }
    .section-navy { background: var(--color-navy); }
    .section-cream { background: var(--color-cream); }

    .section-header {
      max-width: 680px;
      margin-bottom: 48px;
    }
    .section-header.center {
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .section-header h2 { margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .section-header p { color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 1.05rem; }
    .section-navy .section-header h2 { color: var(--color-white); }
    .section-navy .section-header p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); }
    .section-navy .section-label { color: var(--color-gold-light); }

    /* ============================================================
       SECTION 1: ROUTES COMPARISON
    ============================================================ */
    .routes-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
      gap: 24px;
    }
    .route-card {
      background: var(--color-white);
      border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
      transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    .route-card:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: var(--shadow-lift); }
    .route-card.featured { border-color: var(--color-gold); border-width: 2px; }
    .route-card-top {
      padding: 22px 22px 18px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    }
    .route-card.featured .route-card-top { background: var(--color-navy); }
    .route-card-number {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      color: var(--color-gold);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .route-card.featured .route-card-number { color: var(--color-gold-light); }
    .route-card-title {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      color: var(--color-navy);
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    .route-card.featured .route-card-title { color: var(--color-white); }
    .route-card-desc {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: var(--color-text-muted);
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .route-card.featured .route-card-desc { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); }
    .route-card-body {
      padding: 18px 22px 22px;
      flex: 1;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .route-stat {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: baseline;
      padding-bottom: 10px;
      border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--color-border);
    }
    .route-stat:last-of-type { border-bottom: none; }
    .route-stat-key {
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      color: var(--color-text-muted);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .route-stat-val {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--color-navy);
      text-align: right;
      max-width: 55%;
    }
    .featured-ribbon {
      background: var(--color-gold);
      color: var(--color-white);
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 5px;
    }

    /* ============================================================
       SECTION 2: TIMELINE
    ============================================================ */
    .timeline { position: relative; padding-left: 36px; }
    .timeline::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      left: 11px;
      top: 0; bottom: 0;
      width: 2px;
      background: var(--color-border);
    }
    .timeline-item {
      position: relative;
      padding-bottom: 36px;
    }
    .timeline-item:last-child { padding-bottom: 0; }
    .timeline-dot {
      position: absolute;
      left: -36px;
      top: 4px;
      width: 24px; height: 24px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--color-gold);
      border: 3px solid var(--color-cream);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(200,146,42,0.2);
    }
    .timeline-dot-num {
      font-size: 0.65rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--color-white);
    }
    .timeline-phase {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--color-gold);
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .timeline-title {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: var(--color-navy);
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    .timeline-body {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--color-text-muted);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .timeline-duration {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 5px;
      margin-top: 8px;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--color-navy);
      background: var(--color-cream-dark);
      border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 3px 10px;
    }
    .timeline-aside {
      background: var(--color-navy);
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      padding: 28px;
      height: fit-content;
    }
    .timeline-aside-title {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      color: var(--color-white);
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      padding-bottom: 14px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
    }
    .aside-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 9px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    }
    .aside-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .aside-key { font-size: 0.82rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); }
    .aside-val { font-size: 0.88rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-white); }
    .expedite-banner {
      margin-top: 20px;
      background: rgba(200,146,42,0.15);
      border: 1px solid rgba(200,146,42,0.3);
      border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
      padding: 14px;
    }
    .expedite-banner-label {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--color-gold-light);
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    .expedite-banner-text {
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    /* Two-column layout helper */
    .two-col {
      display: grid;
