                <p class="timeline-body">Determine which of the four Ministry of Public Security categories applies to you: Investment-Based, Employment-Based, Special Contributions, or Family Reunion. Review income documentation, tax records, employment contracts, and residency history against the criteria your city tier applies.</p>
