                <p class="timeline-body">Local PSB conducts an investigation (up to 3 months) and the inspection authority reviews the dossier (up to 2 months). The National Immigration Administration grants final approval. Any request for supplementary evidence (RFE) should be answered promptly to keep the file moving.</p>
